        "subject": "LU-822 osd: decrease OI files number to 32",
        "message": "LU-822 osd: decrease OI files number to 32\n\nTest results (attached on LU-822) show that 32 OI files can give\nsame performance as 64 OI files over ldiskfs. Also, 32 OI files can\ngive better performance than 64 OIs over ZFS, so we decrease default\nnumber of OI files from 32 to 64.\n\nSigned-off-by: Liang Zhen <liang@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: Ie58fc600f94b4fba67d519b69c4894214a35f065\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
